description: Social democrat Zoran Milanovic wins a run-off vote in a blow to the nationalist HDZ party.
title: Croatia elects centre-left challenger Zoran Milanovic as president
title_page: Croatia elects centre-left challenger Zoran Milanovic as president - BBC News
maintext: Mr Milanovic, who will take office on 19 February, will have a higher profile as president than usual, as Croatia has just taken over the rotating presidency of the EU for six months.
